        "gg8UTtxkN-D_text": "<s>$29</s> FREE&nbsp;",
        "ggTwHTgH5lQ_text": "This expert-backed eBook with 100+ pages of value-packed info covers <strong>how to best use your Triple Fusion Massager</strong>, as well as proven techniques, exercises, and <strong>lifestyle tips</strong> to help you <strong>eliminate pain and get your life back naturally.</strong>",
