        "gg9sfrUDNiv_text": "Relief in 3 Simple Steps.",
        "ggFoLsfJU5j_text": "<p>Just put the Red Light Therapy Belt on, choose your mode and intensity, and enjoy the effect!</p>",
        "ggNDYVqN7Gc_text": "Relief in 3 Simple Steps.",
        "ggNxAHEd9SQ_text": "<p>While you sit, cook, or even take a walk around the house, the belt works on three levels:</p>",
        "ggP9YY587P1_text": "<p><strong>Boosting blood flow and oxygen delivery</strong></p>",
        "gg_-MJSPsBq_text": "<p><strong>Releasing pressure on the sciatic nerve</strong></p>",
        "ggb3x-tTKfi_html5Url": "https://cdn.shopify.com/videos/c/o/v/438845eea3424c84a61445e1fdbc2042.mov",
