        "ggmciU_MO8m_text": "<p>— Jennifer S.</p>",
        "ggnkoHZd9S5_text": "<p>\"I’ve been using heating pads for years, and while they felt good in the moment, the pain always came back the second I stood up. I didn’t believe anything portable could go deeper. But after two weeks with the SmoothSpine Therapy Belt, I can honestly say it’s night and day. The combination of heat, vibration, and light therapy gives lasting relief. I finally wake up without stiffness.\"</p>",
